{"tid":2040267,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"司法機構：李瀚良法官聯署後已避嫌 並指投訴案件中律政司未有要求其避席","createTime":"2020-05-28T12:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T14:07:44.000Z","uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"73f80b8d195f8e20dbe472ae40ea2b87e4a70c0b","tid":2040267,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:49:40.000Z","msg":"高院法官李瀚良自聯署反逃犯條例後無獲安排處理相關案件<br />\n28.05.2020 20:42<br />\n<br />\n司法機構表示，高等法院法官李瀚良，在去年6月簽署撤回逃犯條例的聯署後，並未獲安排處理與聲明有關議題的案件。司法機構指，有關安排是根據《法官行為指引》避免審理案件時有表面偏頗的情況。李瀚良在去年10月1日，擔任當值法官，處理緊急申請時，處理過一宗人身保護令申請，<span style=\"color: gold;\">聆訊時律政司代表並沒有要求李瀚良避席</span>，亦不反對人身保護令的申請，除此之外，他並無處理和聯署有關的案件。<br />\n<br />\n李瀚良是在去年6月，簽署3千多名港大畢業生聯署，題為《反對謊言施政 撤回引渡惡法》聯署聲明。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1292710&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1292710%26csid%3D261_341&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu5szS%2Fgy1fqSqMk7TcT3QhU%3D&h=7b8d180e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1292710&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"1e8ae384bf403852eb748a3e651544535d2bb230","tid":2040267,"uid":49329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:19:23.000Z","msg":"惟一講人話嘅法官"},{"pid":"1a0afc3d36846faee0d3e62d76f75a9a7fe9ce26","tid":2040267,"uid":212717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304dbde8e59b450eb2d3db2737f06d8db032b4e8","tid":2040267,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a0afc3d36846faee0d3e62d76f75a9a7fe9ce26","tid":2040267,"uid":212717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T13:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T14:07:44.000Z","msg":"佢有 cancer..